--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Music notation rendering and playback use alphaTab (@coderline/alphatab),
(c) Daniel Kuschny and contributors, under the Mozilla Public License 2.0.
alphaTab is used as an unmodified dependency. Its source is available at
https://github.com/CoderLine/alphaTab. If alphaTab's own source files are
modified, those file-level changes must be made available under the MPL-2.0.

