Chord voicing data — @tombatossals/chords-db (MIT)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Guitar and ukulele chord shapes are derived from @tombatossals/chords-db,
used under the MIT license. See packages/music-core/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.

