Native image processing — libvips via sharp (LGPL-3.0-or-later)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Build-time and server-side image optimization use sharp (Apache-2.0), which
dynamically links the prebuilt libvips native library (@img/sharp-libvips-*),
licensed under LGPL-3.0-or-later. libvips is used unmodified as a dynamically
linked, prebuilt binary.

